org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.vector.impl

Class DelegatingNamedVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.vector.impl.DelegatingVector
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.math.primitives.vector.impl.DelegatingNamedVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Destroyable, MetaAttributes, NamedVector, Vector, StorageOpsMetrics

    public class DelegatingNamedVector
extends DelegatingVector
implements NamedVector
    Delegating named vector that delegates all operations to underlying vector and adds implementation of NamedVector functionality using embedded map that maps string index on real integer index.
    See Also:
